Class RegisterUserMapper

java.lang.Object
com.cafe.backend.entity.mapper.RegisterUserMapper
public class RegisterUserMapper extends Object
RegisterUserMapper is a utility class used for mapping between RegisterUserDTO and UserEntity. This class provides a method to convert a RegisterUserDTO to a UserEntity.

The class has a private constructor to prevent instantiation as it only contains static utility methods.
